支那海岸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa879335447a121bf05c712fa9cec3e906b2331c","tid":2495260,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"呢D唔係用來打對岸, 係用來對抗中共D導彈飽和攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n像科幻片 美軍大炮準確擊落巡航導彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2193511/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2193511/page/1</a>"}]}